Venezuela

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:43.220
Argentina

00:00:43.460 --> 00:00:44.580
Brasil

00:00:44.820 --> 00:00:45.660
India

00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:47.040
Turquía

00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:48.200
